room_title: Escape room "Banshee!" by Minute 59 Mystery and Escape Rooms in Bemidji
room_address: 802 Paul Bunyan Dr SE #17, Bemidji, MN 56601
room_description: A Banshee with a vendetta against your village has been taking villagers one by one, turning them into her eternal minions. Your group has decided something needs to be done! The only way to stop her is to steal her silver comb, the source of her power over her servants. But to do that, you must enter her lair. You have one hour before she rises to claim another victim. Your quest is for the future of your village!
